{
  "_comment": "Bundled color palettes for the statusline-theme skill. Each palette has 9 ROLES (text, muted, red, peach, yellow, green, sky, blue, mauve) as #RRGGBB. The 'apply palette' mode maps each statusline color KEY -> a ROLE using rolemap.json, then resolves the role to the hex below. Hex values were verified against each project's authoritative source. Some palettes have no distinct color for every role; in those cases the closest named color is reused (noted in _notes).",
  "_notes": "Monokai has no separate blue (cyan #66d9ef serves sky+blue). Rose Pine: gold #f6c177 serves peach+yellow, foam #9ccfd8 serves sky+blue, pine #31748f is green. Solarized dark/light share the same accent hues; only text/muted differ. One Dark red uses the canonical Atom One Dark hue-5 (#e06c75).",

